15. Root Cause Analysis (RCA)

Never finish an incident by saying:

Restarted server.

Instead answer:

Why did it happen?

Example RCA:

Problem

Website unavailable

Reason

Disk became full

Cause

Application generated excessive logs

Solution

Deleted logs

Prevention

Configure log rotation

Always identify:

Immediate cause
Root cause
Preventive action
