Monitor disk usage
Add alerting for disk utilization
Biggest Mistakes Engineers Make
❌ Mistake 1

Restarting services immediately.

Always inspect logs first.

❌ Mistake 2

Ignoring monitoring alerts.

Alerts provide valuable clues about timing and affected components.

❌ Mistake 3

Not documenting what happened.

Without notes, RCA becomes difficult.

❌ Mistake 4

Fixing symptoms instead of identifying the root cause.

A restart may restore service temporarily but won't prevent recurrence.

